package commands
  • Class
    Description
    Add
    Class, which is responsible for adding new element into the collection
    AddIfMin
    Class, which is responsible for adding new element into the collection if it's minimal
    Clear
    Class, which is responsible for clearing your collection by deleting all the elements
    Command
    Basic interface for each command of working with collection
    ExecuteScript
    Class, which is responsible for executing script from entered file
    Exit
    Class, which is responsible for exiting from the program
    FilterGreaterThanDifficulty
    Class, which is responsible for printing elements with greater difficulty than set
    FilterLessThanMaximumPoint
    Class, which is responsible for printing elements with less max points than set
    Head
    Class, which is responsible for printing first element of the collection
    Help
    Class, which is responsible for giving information about available commands
    Info
    Class, which is responsible for giving information about current elements in the collection
    PrintFieldDescendingDiscipline
    Class, which is responsible for printing elements in descending order sorted by the disciplines of LabWorks
    RemoveByID
    Class, which is responsible for removing element by set ID
    RemoveLower
    Class, which is responsible for removing lower element than set
    Save
    Class, which is responsible for saving your collection into the XML file
    Show
    Class, which is responsible for showing current elements in the collection
    UpdateByID
    Class, which is responsible for updating element of collection by set ID
